1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:04,500
Welcome to KapiMart — your new favorite online store.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:09,000
In this quick tour, we'll show you how to find products,
place orders, and track your deliveries.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:14,500
Start by browsing our categories. We've organized everything
from electronics to kitchen essentials.

4
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:19,000
Found something you like? Click "Add to Cart" to save it.
You can keep shopping or check out right away.

5
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:24,500
At checkout, enter your shipping address and payment details.
We accept all major credit cards and digital wallets.

6
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:29,000
Once your order is placed, you'll receive a confirmation email
with a tracking number.

7
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:34,500
Track your package in real time from the "Order History" page.
You'll get notifications at every step.

8
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:39,000
Need to return something? No problem.
Go to your order, click "Return Item," and follow the steps.

9
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:44,500
Our support team is available around the clock.
Reach us via chat, email, or phone — whatever works for you.

10
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:49,000
That's it! You're all set to start shopping.
Enjoy free shipping on your first order with code WELCOME.
